.DS_Store
# Runtime/generated tool packages are not Agentic platform source.
# The core stores tool manifests/versions/settings/status in metadata stores
# and passes only enabled/available registrations to agents. Package source
# under tools/ is operator/runtime data used to build or run separate
# source-bundle/OCI/external tool services.
/tools/
workspace/*
!workspace/.gitkeep
